  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00018', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-114-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-05', NULL, 'essay', '甲高齡 90歲欲交代後事，乃偕同兩位適格的見證人乙、丙，親至公證處
辦理公證遺囑。公證人依甲所陳述的內容，以電腦打字方式製作公證書。
除向甲、乙、丙在場人宣讀、講解遺囑內容，經甲認可後，記明日期。
最後請甲簽名時，甲表示其很久沒寫字了，已經不會簽名。公證人則代
書甲姓名，並將常用的橡皮圖章「不識文字，不能簽名」蓋在事由欄，
使甲親自按指印，再由公證人與乙、丙兩位見證人同行簽名。請問此份
公證遺囑是否有效？（35分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "946a97990c95", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114120", "c": "101", "s": "0401", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "民法", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "公證人"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00019', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-114-f9fb6a06', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-06', NULL, 'essay', '英譯中：請將下列這段英文譯成正確、流暢的中文（30 分）
Fanbehaviorrepresentsacomplexinterplayofpsychological,social,and
cultural factors. It encompasses a range of practices, including attending live
events, consuming and promoting related media, and participating in online
andofflinecommunities.Suchbehaviorsoftenfosterasenseofbelongingand
collective identity, reinforcing social bonds among individuals with shared
interests. From a sociocultural perspective, fandom can be seen as a site of
meaning-making where fans actively construct and negotiate their identities.
However, maladaptive fan behavior may include obsession, hostility toward
rivals,orintrusionsonpublicfigures.Asfandomsincreasinglyoperatewithin
digital spaces, scholars emphasize the need to examine how technological
affordancesamplifybothpositiveengagementandproblematicpractices,with
implicationsforculturalproduction and socialdynamics.', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "132a6fc76eeb", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114120", "c": "101", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "英文", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "公證人"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00020', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-114-f9fb6a06', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-06', NULL, 'essay', '中譯英：請將下列這段中文譯成正確、流暢的英文（30 分）
水資源短缺已成為影響數十億人口的全球性挑戰。氣候變遷、人口增
長及非永續的水資源管理等因素加劇了對這一關鍵資源的競爭。在許多
地區，清潔水的獲取依然受限，導致健康危機、糧食不安全，以及圍繞水
權的衝突。情況在乾旱和半乾旱地區尤為嚴峻，該些地區的乾旱發生頻率
和嚴重程度正不斷增加中。應對水資源短缺需要整合水資源管理、投資永
續基礎設施，並進行國際合作以確保公平分配。長期解決方案也須優先考
量生態系統保護和技術創新，包括水資源回收與海水淡化。', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "132a6fc76eeb", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114120", "c": "101", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "英文", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "公證人"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00021', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-114-f9fb6a06', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-06', NULL, 'essay', '英文作文：請根據下列說明寫一篇約 250-300字的英文作文（40分）
