providing universal access to healthcare remains a challenge in many
countries due to economic and political constraints. Write a short essay of
250–300 words to (1) discuss the reasons why healthcare is widely regarded
as a basic human right, and (2) share your opinion on how nations can
realisticallybalancethisidealwith limited resources.', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "132a6fc76eeb", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114120", "c": "101", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "英文", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "公證人"}'::jsonb, NULL),
